    • 方法详细资料

      • setConsoleLogLevel

        public static void setConsoleLogLevel(AylaLog.LogLevel logLevel)
        Set console log level for Ayla logs. Logs will be displayed on the console only if the log level in the message is higher priority than the saved console log level.
        参数:
        logLevel - Log level

      • setFileLogLevel

        public static void setFileLogLevel(AylaLog.LogLevel logLevel)
        Set file log level for Ayla logs. Logs will be saved to log files only if the log level in the message is higher priority than the saved file log level.
        参数:
        logLevel - Log level

      • initAylaLog

        public static void initAylaLog(java.lang.String sessionName,
                               java.lang.String fileName,
                               AylaLog.LogLevel consoleLevel,
                               AylaLog.LogLevel fileLevel)
        Initialize AylaLog. Sets default log level for console and file loggers.

      • uploadLogsToLogService

        public static AylaAPIRequest uploadLogsToLogService(com.android.volley.Response.Listener<AylaAPIRequest.EmptyResponse> successListener,
                                                    ErrorListener errorListener)
        Uploads logs generated from this app to Ayla Log service.
        参数:
        successListener - Listener to be called on successful logs upload.
        errorListener - Listener to be called if an error occurs.
        返回:
        cancelable AylaAPIRequest.
